### Master of Science thesis
This is my master of science dissertation/thesis in Computational Modeling and Scientific Computing.
Yet another useful way to use GitHub :)

### What is it about?
Transforming Boolean models into semicontinuous ones involving parameter estimation, featuring evolutionary computation
